QuestData.Title: Return to the Marsh
QuestData.Description: Return to Ysiel and let her know that help will be extended to her as soon as it is possible.$B$BAffairs in Moonglade and Silithus have kept our members occupied, but we will do our best to send the necessary resources to the Cenarion Refuge.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Ysiel Windsinger at the Cenarion Refuge in Zangarmarsh.
QuestData.RewardText: You are a welcome sight, $n. Matters at the Cenarion Refuge have only gotten worse since you left.
